English Question:
If f(x) = \sqrt{x} -
 i. f'(x) = \frac{1}{2\sqrt{x}}
 ii. \int_{0}^{1} f(x) dx = \frac{2}{3}
 iii. \int \frac{sec^{2}x}{f(tanx)} dx =\frac{1}{2} \sqrt{tanx} + c
 Which one is correct?

Bengali Question:
f(x) = \sqrt{x} হলে-
 i. f'(x) = \frac{1}{2\sqrt{x}}
 ii. \int_{0}^{1} f(x) dx = \frac{2}{3}
 iii. \int \frac{sec^{2}x}{f(tanx)} dx =\frac{1}{2} \sqrt{tanx} + c
 নিচের কোনটি সঠিক?

